content: I'll definitely try out these techniques, thanks for the detailed guide. I've been watching some YouTube tutorials on model building, particularly from a channel called "Model Mastery," and I've learned a lot of new techniques from his videos. By the way, I recently finished building a 1/48 scale F-16 jet fighter model, and I'm really happy with how it turned out, especially the intricate details on the cockpit and the paint job.
